      <EnglishText>&lt;Arche&gt;</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53412,53628,53856,53972,54096,54828</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>アルベルト</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Albert</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53740,54292,54500,54712</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Chester&gt;</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょ、ちょ、ちょっと！　なんか言いなさいよ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wait a second! Say something, you!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53416</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ～～、なんだぁ？　おら忙しいだーよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whatcha want? I'm busy, make it short.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人の顔見て、ため息ついて。いったいなんなのよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You just show up on new people's faces without saying a word? What sort of weirdo does that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53632</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そったらことがえ？
あんまりにも、期待外れだったもんでよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that what it looks like? Here's some news for you miss, this is the face of disappointment...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何に期待して、出てきたんだよ？
前に会ったんじゃないのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And what exactly where you expecting? You don't mean you met her before, do you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きらめきの塔の時は、
おら&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;の胸にうずもれてただ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh I've taken a peek back in Glimmer Spire while buried under &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;'s bosom.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>53976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もっと、こう元気印のハツラツな娘っ子だと
思ってただーよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I thought I'd meet a lively charming young lady, full of energy and love for this world...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>54100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それが、こ～んな女として
魅力の欠片もねぇとんだすれっからしとは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yet this excuse of a woman standing next to me isn't even a fraction of charming as what I had in mind...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>54164</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wait a sec—</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>54296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いい加減にしろ！　&lt;Arche&gt;のこと、
何も知らないくせに勝手なこと、言うんじゃねぇ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ok that's enough jabbering, pal! You don't know the first thing about &lt;Arche&gt; so do me a favor and shut that pie hole!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>54360</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Chester&gt;...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>54504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>確かにすぐに怒るし、おしゃべりだし、素直じゃ
ないし、胸もない、料理も下手、だけどなぁ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah she gets angry quickly, is a loudmouth, has no manners, is as flat as it gets, can't cook and so on but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>54572</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;のバカ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Chester&gt;, you idiot!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>54716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……だけど、そういうところが悪くないって、
言おうと思ったのに……オレってしまらねぇな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Yet she's not a bad person at all...is what I wanted to say. Damn I screwed up...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>54832</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_074_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ただの凶暴なオバハンだでよ……
くわばら、くわばら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Sounds like a regular old grandma to me. Shame on you. Shame on you...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
